sections.heading: to 2-8C-49 - Repealed.
sections.text: Repeals.— Laws 2002, ch. 98. § 50 repealed 2-8C-1 to 2-8C-49 NMSA 1978, as enacted by Laws 1991 (1st S.S.), ch. 3, § 1, relating to the 1991 Senate Redistricting Act, effective May 15, 2002. For provisions of former sections,seethe 2001 NMSA 1978 onNMOneSource.com.
